title: Beowulf, Translated and read by Seamus Heany, 2000

Beowulf

Translated and read by Seamus Heany, 2000

No more Ray Winston, in his best Albert Square accent drawling

8th century Anglo Saxon epic poem.  Bloodthirst, violent and heroic!
